700
00:40:42,982 --> 00:40:47,185
And losing my husband taught me to value my son.

701
00:40:47,987 --> 00:40:49,938
And when my son was unwell,

702
00:40:50,197 --> 00:40:52,592
I learned to value myself...

703
00:40:52,616 --> 00:40:55,610
so I could take care of him.

704
00:40:55,661 --> 00:40:58,947
And because my life was cut short,

705
00:40:59,582 --> 00:41:03,034
I learned to value everyone here,

706
00:41:03,377 --> 00:41:06,705
