Do you remember this?

1025
01:02:32,999 --> 01:02:35,367
It's the bank book you gave me.

1026
01:02:35,918 --> 01:02:39,189
I wanted to throw this at
your face the next time we met,

1027
01:02:39,213 --> 01:02:41,707
so I didn't spend a single penny.

1028
01:02:42,175 --> 01:02:44,084
But you know what?

1029
01:02:44,135 --> 01:02:46,113
Your mom told me...

1030
01:02:46,137 --> 01:02:50,674
to think of you as a gem
and treat you preciously.

1031
01:02:53,227 --> 01:02:55,080
- Right. Come here.
- What?

1032
01:02:55,104 --> 01:02:56,731
<i><font color="#ffff00">Pig Farm
Office
Welcome, Happy Farm</font></i>

1033
01:02:59,942 --> 01:03:01,768
Take a look.

1034
01:03:02,487 --> 01:03:03,547
Look.

1035
01:03:03,571 --> 01:03:06,732
That's Father, and that's Mother.

1036
01:03:07,033 --> 01:03:09,359
And I love this photo.

1037
01:03:09,869 --> 01:03:12,014
We took this to commemorate...

1038
01:03:12,038 --> 01:03:14,099
the donation we gave under
the name of Happy Farm,

1039
01:03:14,123 --> 01:03:16,297
after receiving a prize
for our pig farm business.

1040
01:03:16,321 --> 01:03:18,061
This was such a proud moment, wasn't it?

1041
01:03:18,085 --> 01:03:20,049
It was.

1042
01:03:22,715 --> 01:03:26,793
This is the cutest photo of
you taken on your first birthday.

1043
01:03:29,889 --> 01:03:33,425
And that's a photo of your parents' wedding.

1044
01:03:33,476 --> 01:03:35,344
And...

1045
01:03:35,478 --> 01:03:40,918
I thought long and hard about
what photo to hang next to it.

1046
01:03:40,942 --> 01:03:42,669
And I think...

1047
01:03:42,693 --> 01:03:46,632
it'd be nice to hang
something similar to this one.

1048
01:03:46,656 --> 01:03:49,218
If you have any good ideas, let me know.

1049
01:03:49,242 --> 01:03:51,762
Okay?

1050
01:03:51,786 --> 01:03:53,737
- Next to that one?
- Yes.

1051
01:03:55,540 --> 01:03:57,768
Get changed.

1052
01:03:57,792 --> 01:03:59,326
Okay.

1053
01:04:32,368 --> 01:04:35,404
<i>To my beloved son, Kang-ho.</i>

1054
01:04:35,872 --> 01:04:40,742
<i>Do you remember the very first
letter you'd written to me?</i>

1055
01:04:41,127 --> 01:04:44,565
<i>"We may be apart,"</i>

1056
01:04:44,589 --> 01:04:49,403
<i>"but I still live..."</i>

1057
01:04:49,427 --> 01:04:53,964
<i>"in the memories I shared with you and Father."</i>

1058
01:04:55,558 --> 01:04:58,620
<i>By the time you read this letter,</i>

1059
01:04:58,644 --> 01:05:01,638
<i>I'll be feeling the same.</i>

1060
01:05:02,565 --> 01:05:04,391
<i>Kang-ho.</i>

1061
01:05:04,567 --> 01:05:06,712
<i>The Chinese character for "connection"...</i>

1062
01:05:06,736 --> 01:05:11,440
<i>contains the characters
for "thread" and "pig head."</i>

1063
01:05:12,033 --> 01:05:16,528
<i>The connections we build with
others are just as difficult...</i>

1064
01:05:16,579 --> 01:05:19,531
<i>as leading a pig with a thread.</i>

1065
01:05:20,499 --> 01:05:27,998
<i>We were connected as mother and son.</i>

1066
01:05:29,258 --> 01:05:31,528
<i>It's such a precious bond,</i>

1067
01:05:31,552 --> 01:05:35,297
<i>so I wanted to become the best mom for you.</i>

1068
01:05:35,848 --> 01:05:37,784
<i>But you only get one life,</i>

1069
01:05:37,808 --> 01:05:40,370
<i>and it was my first time being a mom,</i>

1070
01:05:40,394 --> 01:05:44,848
<i>so I'm sorry I wasn't good enough.</i>

1071
01:05:45,983 --> 01:05:49,686
<i>I made a wish before blowing
out my birthday candles.</i>

1072
01:05:49,987 --> 01:05:54,900
<i>I prayed that I'd become your mom once again.</i>

1073
01:05:56,661 --> 01:05:58,513
<i>If that ever happens,</i>

1074
01:05:58,537 --> 01:06:01,281
<i>I promise to be a better mom.</i>

1075
01:06:05,419 --> 01:06:10,040
<i>I won't tell you not to be
sad about not having a dad.</i>

1076
01:06:10,424 --> 01:06:14,628
<i>I won't say that your grades
are all that matters in life.</i>

1077
01:06:15,763 --> 01:06:20,008
<i>I won't ignore your talent for drawing.</i>

1078
01:06:20,935 --> 01:06:24,706
<i>I won't turn away...</i>

1079
01:06:24,730 --> 01:06:27,224
<i>when I know you want to eat more.</i>

1080
01:06:28,109 --> 01:06:30,212
<i>I won't hold back my tears...</i>

1081
01:06:30,236 --> 01:06:32,979
<i>when I see you in pain.</i>

1082
01:06:33,239 --> 01:06:36,343
<i>I'll help you get up when you fall.</i>

1083
01:06:36,367 --> 01:06:38,777
<i>I'll embrace you when you're afraid.</i>

1084
01:06:40,037 --> 01:06:42,349
<i>I'll say, "Good job,"</i>

1085
01:06:42,373 --> 01:06:44,116
<i>"thank you,"</i>

1086
01:06:44,375 --> 01:06:46,535
<i>and "I love you,"</i>

1087
01:06:46,836 --> 01:06:49,246
<i>every single day.</i>

1088
01:06:50,756 --> 01:06:52,651
<i>And I won't...</i>

1089
01:06:52,675 --> 01:06:55,544
<i>leave you so soon.</i>

1090
01:06:57,054 --> 01:06:59,172
<i>I love you, my son.</i>

1091
01:07:00,516 --> 01:07:04,121
<i>I hope you live a long, happy life...</i>

1092
01:07:04,145 --> 01:07:07,431
<i>with Mi-joo, Seo-jin, and Ye-jin.</i>

1093
01:07:08,024 --> 01:07:11,101
<i>And we'll meet again...</i>

1094
01:07:11,235 --> 01:07:14,271
<i>on the day my prayer is answered.</i>

1095
01:07:15,197 --> 01:07:17,649
<i>From your bad mother.</i>

1096
01:07:44,351 --> 01:07:46,303
Today...

1097
01:07:47,063 --> 01:07:50,682
is the day I propose to Mi-joo...

1098
01:07:51,108 --> 01:07:54,144
to ask her to live a long
and happy life with me.

1099
01:07:55,279 --> 01:07:57,689
But you ruined everything.

1100
01:08:04,705 --> 01:08:07,407
Please watch over me...

1101
01:08:07,833 --> 01:08:10,035
so I won't be too nervous.

1102
01:08:11,128 --> 01:08:12,871
No.

1103
01:08:14,507 --> 01:08:16,583
Protect us.

1104
01:08:24,934 --> 01:08:26,676
Lee Mi-joo!

1105
01:08:26,852 --> 01:08:30,749
You're under arrest for becoming my wife!

1106
01:08:30,773 --> 01:08:34,169
You don't have the right to remain silent.

1107
01:08:34,193 --> 01:08:36,463
You can't ask your mother
for help when we argue.

1108
01:08:36,487 --> 01:08:37,839
How childish.

1109
01:08:37,863 --> 01:08:40,383
This isn't a proposal.

1110
01:08:40,407 --> 01:08:42,859
- Why not?
- What you just said...

1111
01:08:42,910 --> 01:08:44,930
might be used against you later in life.

1112
01:08:44,954 --> 01:08:46,947
So watch out, okay?

1113
01:08:48,415 --> 01:08:49,976
- This won't do.
- What?

1114
01:08:50,000 --> 01:08:52,187
All right. I need your help.

1115
01:08:52,211 --> 01:08:53,912
- What?
- All right.

1116
01:08:57,801 --> 01:08:58,777
Lee Mi-joo!

1117
01:08:58,801 --> 01:09:00,821
I saved your life three times.

1118
01:09:00,845 --> 01:09:02,739
So even if I get so annoying,

1119
01:09:02,763 --> 01:09:04,241
even if we argue,

1120
01:09:04,265 --> 01:09:07,300
and even if I get downright childish,

1121
01:09:08,185 --> 01:09:12,514
promise to live with me
happily the rest of our lives.

1122
01:09:18,112 --> 01:09:19,506
All right, go ahead.

1123
01:09:19,530 --> 01:09:20,882
- Come here.
- Go to mommy.

1124
01:09:20,906 --> 01:09:24,359
- No!
- Oh, no!

1125
01:10:02,865 --> 01:10:06,261
- Kang-ho! Hang on, I...
- We have to look good.

1126
01:10:06,285 --> 01:10:09,723
Come on, think of our age.

1127
01:10:09,747 --> 01:10:13,059
♫ <i>He's a napa cabbage flower
Napa cabbage flower</i> ♫

1128
01:10:13,083 --> 01:10:17,814
{\an8}♫ <i>A new wind will blow</i> ♫

1129
01:10:17,838 --> 01:10:18,857
{\an8}<i><font color="#ffff00">Sam-sik's Mill</font></i>

1130
01:10:18,881 --> 01:10:21,776
{\an8}I don't even eat marinated crab,

1131
01:10:21,800 --> 01:10:23,670
{\an8}because it's so good I'd steal to eat them!

1132
01:10:23,694 --> 01:10:24,912
{\an8}I hate stray cats even more.

1133
01:10:24,936 --> 01:10:26,698
{\an8}They're like little thieves.

1134
01:10:26,722 --> 01:10:29,242
{\an8}Do you know how shocked I was...

1135
01:10:29,266 --> 01:10:31,578
{\an8}when "The Thieves" was released?

1136
01:10:31,602 --> 01:10:34,012
{\an8}Hey!

